         "title":{
            "en":"Let us challenge you now!"
         },
         "text":{
            "en":"Which two standard gears from your kit can generate a 3:1 Teeth Ratio? How will this Teeth Ratio affect speed and torque?"
         },
         "type":"horizontal"
      },
      {
         "id":"64976043-f265-44cf-912d-52fbfdf86096",
         "title":{
            "en":"Let us challenge you now!"
